patthana16.7:1.1_0: Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naabyākatassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena
patthana16.7:1.1_1: paccayo. Abyākato appaccayo dhammo nakusalassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena
patthana16.7:1.1_2: paccayo. Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naakusalassa naappaccayassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena
patthana16.7:1.1_3: paccayo. Abyākato appaccayo dhammo naakusalassa naappaccayassa ca naabyākatassa naappaccayassa
patthana16.7:1.1_4: ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Abyākato appaccayo dhammo nakusalassa naappaccayassa
patthana16.7:1.1_5: ca naakusalassa naappaccayassa ca dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo.
patthana16.7:2.1: Ārammaṇe pañca, adhipatiyā upanissaye pañca. (Asaṅkhataṁ appaccayasadisaṁ.)
